	DHH’s existing website – designed in 2023, was attempting to stand out among other providers of The Horse Course with its unique appearance. However, it did not reflect the founder’s distinct outlook, it wasn’t optimised for mobile, and it wasn’t driving donations.
	It was time for a change.
	{{ carousel({ carouselId: "DHH1",
