</div>
<div class="article-section">
	<h3 id="challenge">Challenge</h3>
	Rebrand, Redesign, Relaunch
	Our goal was to create a page that would properly showcase DHH’s work to funders and donors. However, we were aiming to be more than a donation page – we were also striving to create a welcoming place for potential participants and referrers.
</div>
<div class="article-section">
	<h3 id="questions">Questions to Answer</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>
			Who are Devon Healing Horsemanship?
		</li>
		<li>
			What makes DHH's work so effective?
		</li>
		<li>
