<h2 id="informative-design">Informative Design</h2>
<div class="article-section">
	<h3 id="landing-page">Landing Page Elevator Pitch</h3>
	The original site did not sell itself as well as its competitors. At a glance, it was difficult to tell who this service was for and what its benefits were.
	
	{{ carousel({ carouselId: "DHH4",
