	As a locally focussed charity, it was important that people could get to know the team that they would be entrusting with their time, money and community. The original page featured a mission statement and a bit about the team and their values as a whole. However, it didn’t introduce the team – or the horses – as individuals.
	
	{{ carousel({ carouselId: "DHH7",
