	<h4>On-site Widget</h4>
	Donors appreciate knowing the impact of their generosity. To encourage this, we created a widget that allows for monthly and one-off donations. The widget offers suggested payment amounts, with short descriptions of what that donation can cover.
	{{ carousel({ carouselId: "DHH12",
							images: [
